          "default": "Truth is to be given when needed and this company was very easy to work with. The quality of the product is good, very easy to assemble and what I was even more impressed with was the quality of the printing they do on the fabric."
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "presets": [
    {
      "name": "Customer Reviews",
      "blocks": [
        { "type": "review", "settings": { "reviewer_name": "Joni Dasilva", "review_date": "04/06/2026", "title": "Premium straight tension fabric backdrop display", "body": "Truth is to be given when needed and this company was very easy to work with. The quality of the product is good, very easy to assemble and what I was even more impressed with was the quality of the printing they do on the fabric. Granted the quality of your picture needs to be top notch in order for the print to look perfect." } },
        { "type": "review", "settings": { "reviewer_name": "Kateryna Rybakina", "review_date": "03/11/2026", "title": "Stunning quality, very satisfied", "body": "The fabric stretched perfectly over the frame, the structure became remarkably stable. Colors were vibrant. Very good quality. Quick turn around and delivery. highly recommended." } }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}